{"tid":1301372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東省交通廳望放寬港珠澳大橋車輛配額","createTime":"2019-07-09T15:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T03:15:10.000Z","uid":127569,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c030eab71733c57493792fd2a13d2606d6293e1d","tid":1301372,"uid":127569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:26:02.000Z","msg":"廣東省交通廳表示，現行因受制於港珠澳大橋的配額政策影響，現時大橋及三地口岸設施間協調運作良好，但通行車輛數量與設計時的通行能力仍有差距。為此廣東省將報請國家有關部門，協調兩地牌車輛通行大橋的政策，同時間放寬現有的車輛配額制度，協調並研究放寬大橋的三地通行措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.exmoo.com/article/114575.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.exmoo.com%2Farticle%2F114575.html&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=dbe1dbca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.exmoo.com/article/114575.html</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母風頭火勢仲夠膽死放更多支那車落來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f021bc2a4e39e30267acd59e5f290a373136d64","tid":1301372,"uid":127569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:26:41.000Z","msg":"睇來支那要加速融合香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58975bc19269bf53bc014d51c2a7f2a205b357ad","tid":1301372,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:29:04.000Z","msg":"<code>7.10前 - 一人一信反DQ - Link 1</code><br />\n<code>7.10 - 19:00~22:30 - 麥小姐追思會 ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場🕊️</code><br />\n<code>7.11 - 14:00~22:00 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 ＠ 渣華道遊樂場🕊️</code><br />\n<code>7.11 -  油尖旺區議會夢遊 - Link 2</code><br />\n<code>7.13 - 15:30 - 光復上水 ＠ 上水花園第一號</code><br />\n<code>7.14 - 14:30~15:30 - 沙田區大遊行 ＠ 翠田街足球場</code><br />\n<code>7.21 - 將軍澳遊行</code><br />\n<code>7.27 - 紅磡土瓜灣遊行</code><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><em>Link 1: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/stopDQnow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FstopDQnow&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=6e627904\" data-auto-